      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is strictly for those looking for a project or a parts donor. The engine currently does not turn over, and the transmission is unresponsive, necessitating a complete overhaul or replacement. Additionally, there is significant rust on the undercarriage and the interior shows heavy wear and tear. It is being sold as-is with no guarantees of functionality.",
