    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been consistently well-maintained. The engine is strong and the transmission shifts smoothly, providing a reliable and comfortable driving experience. While there are some minor cosmetic blemishes consistent with its age, such as light surface scratches and minor interior wear, it remains a very solid and dependable car. All major systems are functional, and it has recently undergone a full inspection to ensure it is road-ready.",
